item.title: The Dig - E01 - Hanging out in space
item.description:
The Dig - E01 - Hanging out in space

A deep space adventure by Sean Clark in collaboration with filmmaker Steven Spielberg. A radio telescope in Borneo detects the approach of a large asteroid on a collision course with Earth; authorities dub it "Attila" after the ancient conqueror Attila the Hun. Scientists determine explosives planted on the surface of the asteroid may divert it into a stable orbit around Earth. A five-person expedition use the Space Shuttle Atlantis to rendezvous with the asteroid and plant the charges.
